premise_source_doc_sentence: Hellboy is a 2004 American dark fantasy superhero film directed by Guillermo del Toro and starring Ron Perlman , loosely based on the Dark Horse Comics graphic novel Hellboy : Seed of Destruction by Mike Mignola .
It was ported to the PlayStation as Hellboy : Asylum Seeker , developed by Hoplite Research and released in 2004 .
Hellboy : Dogs of the Night is a 2000 American video game for the PC , developed by Cryo Studios .
Also included on the DVD is the short film Iron Shoes , which is based on the Hellboy story of the same name .
In the film , a demonic beast-turned superhero known as Hellboy , secretly works to keep the world safe from paranormal threats with his team , the Bureau of Paranormal Research and Defense .
